---
export const prerender = true;
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import BottomNav from '../components/BottomNav.astro';
---

<Layout title="Cookie Policy - Mershal" description="Mershal Cookie Policy - Learn about how we use cookies and similar technologies">
  <Header />
  
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12 pb-20 md:pb-8 font-sans text-slate-800">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-serif font-black text-slate-950 mb-3">Cookie Policy</h1>
      
      <div class="bg-slate-100 border-l-4 border-primary-crimson p-4 rounded-r-lg mb-8 shadow-sm">
        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">
          <strong>Last updated:</strong> June 1, 2026
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="prose prose-slate max-w-none text-slate-600 leading-relaxed space-y-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-950 mt-6">What are Cookies?</h2>
        <p>Cookies are small text files placed on your computer or mobile device when you visit a website. They enable features like layout customization, settings retention, and analytics logging. Mershal uses cookies to deliver a better user experience for software builders and founders.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-950 mt-6">How We Use Cookies</h2>
        <p>Mershal uses cookies to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Ensure essential page routing and session stability.</li>
          <li>Remember configuration preferences and dark/light options.</li>
          <li>Analyze traffic trends and software category conversions.</li>
          <li>Serve optimized, relevant ads through partners like Google AdSense.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-950 mt-6">Types of Cookies We Use</h2>
        
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-850 mt-4">1. Essential Cookies</h3>
        <p>Required for secure operation, authentication mechanisms (including our admin controls), and basic navigation features.</p>

        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-850 mt-4">2. Analytics Cookies</h3>
        <p>We leverage tools like Google Analytics to evaluate user journeys, verify reading time metrics, and adjust our content production taxonomy.</p>

        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-850 mt-4">3. Advertising & Marketing Cookies</h3>
        <p>Used to measure advertising performance and help deliver relevant ads to readers interested in tech, business software, and AI.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-950 mt-6">Managing Your Preferences</h2>
        <p>You can choose to opt out of non-essential tracking cookies via our on-site consent manager. Alternatively, configure your browser settings directly to reject cookies:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Chrome:</strong> Settings > Privacy and Security > Third-party cookies</li>
          <li><strong>Firefox:</strong> Settings > Privacy & Security > Cookies and Site Data</li>
          <li><strong>Safari:</strong> Settings > Safari > Advanced > Cookies</li>
          <li><strong>Edge:</strong> Settings > Cookies and site permissions</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-950 mt-6">Updates to This Policy</h2>
        <p>We update this policy periodically to align with evolving digital privacy regulations (GDPR, CCPA) or backend platform modifications.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-950 mt-6">Contact</h2>
        <p>If you have questions regarding this cookie policy, please reach out to us at <a href="mailto:privacy@mershal.in" class="text-primary-crimson hover:underline font-bold">privacy@mershal.in</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  
  <Footer />
  <BottomNav />
</Layout>